l\">Все направления</button>\n<button class=\"whitespace-nowrap px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-navy-text dark:text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all\">Терапия</button>\n<button class=\"whitespace-nowrap px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-navy-text dark:text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all\">Педиатрия</button>\n<button class=\"whitespace-nowrap px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-navy-text dark:text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all\">Дерматология</button>\n<button class=\"whitespace-nowrap px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-navy-text dark:text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all\">Неврология</button>\n<button class=\"whitespace-nowrap px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-navy-text dark:text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all\">Гастроэнтерология</button>\n<button class=\"whitespace-nowrap px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-navy-text dark:text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all\">Кардиология</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-6\">\n<div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-7 rounded-card border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 group cursor-pointer\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start justify-between gap-6\">\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\">\n<span class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-[11px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider\">Неврология</span>\n<div class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-slate-300\"></div>\n<span class=\"text-muted-text text-xs flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">schedule</span> 2 часа назад\n                                </span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy-text dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-tight\">Постоянные головные боли</h3>\n<p class=\"text-muted-text dark:text-slate-400 text-base leading-relaxed line-clamp-2 mb-0\">\n                                Беспокоят мигрени в течение последней недели, сопровождаются тошнотой и светочувствительностью. Анальгетики помогают лишь на короткое время...\n                            </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shrink-0 flex items-start\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary/5 dark:bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-primary/10\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-xl\">forum</span>\n<span class=\"text-primary text-sm font-bold\">3 ответа</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-50 dark:border-slate-800/50 flex items-center justify-between\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n<div class=\"flex -space-x-3\">\n<div class=\"size-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-900 bg-slate-200 overflow-hidden\">\n<img alt=\"Dr.\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDjVxkrbVWQCeHk1ae_EKwLPN0nm-hPIoSzAN9IRuhtC1oz6idbAE71F_iJBIKL7MFEQnN3OZrByYo9xsrpbLV0lQDd_wMOcFIqmVdWW5_CQ8r-wBDYvUUnWjDenZk2qW0KwvLS7C_cS3ZS08y7zUcH_r6Yz_YehEEkL2t8Or8lcKRSIqjIGyFgd-fJ8Kn8gCtszGbrWZj-WxZDJjCWtuR8TzqiUIpGuVYmb15mH7_6rLeqmE_EUYugjry_DexHNt6XpLaQsgRo8r8t\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"size-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-900 bg-slate-200 overflow-hidden\">\n<img alt=\"Dr.\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA_9vqDWrr8WeScQoNUiT9fQxa0QrgvTG1GB9Wy4R73hVgdLeQE4mS2U6vK3g8dVqB-9GymV3I0k4lC8pMK_uEWNKsxmlj7o_vLVznNO9mCPYYBZA24Hz4opY-3-xBH31iknNFr9V7PCxBcz-5SanQyGBQGJS6g2IQqla6TD8MfOFk6jIFi22kFKjvqzLKjPOPeDZ3ndm4_Cu_Kq5Jbc3NVmEjxx9yl-Nv22QK6208upzr-WwVsPi6xE5cBUQh7DB1YVDKLG9tUrI6j\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"size-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-900 bg-slate-400 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-white font-bold\">+1</div>\n</div>\n<span class=\"text-xs text-muted-text font-medium\">Врачи консультируют</span>\n</div>\n<span class=\"text-primary text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:gap-2 transition-all\">\n                            Читать подробнее <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-base\">arrow_forward</span>\n</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-7 rounded-card border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 group cursor-pointer\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start justify-between gap-6\">\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\">\n<span class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-[11px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider\">Педиатрия</span>\n<div class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-slate-300\"></div>\n<span class=\"text-muted-text text-xs flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">schedule</span> 5 часов назад\n                                </span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy-text dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-tight\">Сыпь на руках у ребенка</h3>\n<p class=\"text-muted-text dark:text-slate-400 text-base leading-relaxed line-clamp-2 mb-0\">\n                                Посл